            "type": "text",
            "text": "For API teams aiming to enhance language model capabilities, LTX-2 19B Distilled FP8 a provides an efficient solution with reduced memory overhead via FP8 precision, ideal for latency-sensitive applications. This draft outlines actionable steps for production deployment."
