            "text": "For production scaling, containerize the model using Docker with base images that include CUDA and FP8 support. Deploy on Kubernetes with horizontal pod autoscaling based on CPU/GPU utilization. Implement canary releases to test updates gradually, and use distributed tracing for debugging. Ensure data privacy by encrypting API traffic and validating input schemas to prevent injection attacks. Regularly update model weights and dependencies to incorporate security patches and performance improvements."
